  • Constructor Details

    • MotorConfig

      public MotorConfig(double distanceFactor, double timeFactor, int statorLimit, int supplyLimit, double voltageCompensation, boolean inverted, NAR_Motor.Neutral mode, NAR_Motor.StatusFrames statusFrames)
      Creates a new motor config
      Parameters:
      distanceFactor - Factor to multiply distance units by (per rotations) ie. input circumference for distance
      timeFactor - Factor to multiply time units by (per minutes) ie. use 60 for seconds, 1 for minutes
      statorLimit - The currentLimit for the stator
      supplyLimit - The currentLimit for the motor controller
      voltageCompensation - The voltage compensation for the motor
      inverted - Whether or not the motor is inverted.
      mode - Neutral mode for the motor.
      statusFrames - Status frames for the motor.
